                <h1>Understanding Genetics: Unlocking the Secrets of Heredity</h1>
                <p>Genetics is the study of heredity, focusing on how traits are passed from parents to offspring through genes. It explores DNA structure, gene function, and variations, influencing everything from physical appearance to susceptibility to diseases. Advances in genetics have revolutionized fields like medicine and agriculture, paving the way for genetic engineering and personalized treatments.</p>
